; Three commodities: EUR -> GBP -> $, requiring multi-hop conversion
P 2024/01/01 EUR 0.85 GBP
P 2024/01/01 GBP $1.27

2024/01/15 Test
    Expenses  10 EUR
    Assets

; Convert EUR to $ through GBP via dijkstra path
test bal -X '$'
